---
title: Clare's Soy-Butter Mushroom Bowl with Spring Onion Rice & Peanuts
description: We love a hearty rice bowl! To make things better, this dish is packed with all our veggie favourites, featuring soy butter-glazed portabello mushrooms. It's a deliciously simple and chef-curated recipe (thanks Clare!) that doesn't disappoint.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/clares-soy-butter-mushroom-bowl-6f271197.jpg
